## cdcasestudies Fields

- selectableVariant (string): "default" or "xDemo"
- sortOrder (number): numeric order
- title (string): main heading
- subtitle (string): secondary text
- items (array): list of case study items
  - title (string): item title
  - description (text): item description
  - image (image): optional image
  - link (url): optional link

These fields were selected to display a typical "Case Studies" section.